Package: copulapop
Type: Package
Title: Generate Virtual Populations Using Vine Copulas
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-01-20
Authors@R: person("Rob", "ter Heine", 
                  email = "rob.terheine@radboudumc.nl",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9720-866X"))
Description: Generate realistic virtual patient populations for pharmacometric 
    modeling, PBPK simulations, and clinical trial simulations. Uses R-Vine 
    copulas to preserve complex correlation structures and tail dependencies 
    between covariates. Includes pre-fitted models for international datasets 
    (Netherlands, China, South Korea, Tanzania, USA, UK) with age, height, 
    weight, and optionally creatinine/eGFR. Provides validation report 
    generation to assess copula fit quality.
